---
title: Fig and Brie Cheese Melt with Kale Salad and Sun-dried Tomatoes
description: It’s time to bring your childhood favourite into adulthood. Melty brie is coupled with sweet fig jam creating the ultimate sweet and salty cheesy sandwich. A fresh kale salad is served alongside, with savory slivered sun-dried tomatoes!
